{
  "id": "adv_bond_hrk_01_01",
  "title": "佐伯遙子1",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_library-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_library-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_01-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "（ふぅー……やっとレポート書き終わったー……）\n（今回はちょっと苦戦したわね）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Phew—… I finally finished writing my report—…）\n（This time‚ it was a little difficult）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_library-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_library-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_01-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "（お仕事で出れなかった授業のレジュメを）\n（友達が取っておいてくれて、助かったわ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I was saved when my friend shared a resume of a class）\n（I couldn't attend because of work）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_01-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "（後でお礼しなくちゃね）\n（あ、あそこにいるのは……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I'll have to thank you later）\n（Ah‚ those people over there…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_library-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_library-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_library-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_library-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_01-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "（写真サークルの人達だわ）\n（自分達の作品の品評会してるみたい）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（People in the photography club）\n（It seems like they're holding a design review of their own work）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_01-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "（サークルかぁ……私は所属してないけど）\n（もし入ってたら、どこだったんだろ？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（A club… I don't belong anywhere）\n（If I went in‚ where would it be?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.399998347,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_library-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_library-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.5666650136
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_01-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "（やっぱりキャンプサークルかしら）\n（仲間と焚火を囲んで将来の夢を語る……素敵だわ！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I guess‚ it's a camping club）\n（Sitting around a campfire with friends and talking about dreams for the future… how wonderful!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.5666650136,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-00-night",
      "startTime": 51.4833339691
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_01-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "「こうして焚火の前でゆっくり話すの、いいわよね\n私の将来の夢？　お嫁さんでーす！　ふふ、冗談よ」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "'It feels good to talk leisurely in front of a campfire like this\nMy future dream? To be a bride! Haha‚ just kidding'",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.5333339691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-00-night",
      "startTime": 65.1333339691
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_01-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "「十年後も二十年後も、みんなでキャンプがしたいわ\n私達は一生仲間だもの。ビバ、青春！」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "'I want to go camping with everyone‚ even 10 or 20 years from now\nWe'll be friends forever. Viva‚ youth!'",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.1333339691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_library-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_library-00-noon",
      "startTime": 76.7166622162
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_01-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "（なーんちゃって！　それか、逆にやったことがない）\n（ことをやるのもいいかもしれないわね。例えば――）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Almost said! Because I've never done it before）\n（It might be a good idea to do something. For example――）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.7666622162,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.9499996186
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_01-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "「このハトを3カウント後に消してみせます\n3、2、1……じゃじゃーん！」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "'I'll make this pigeon disappear in 3 counts\n3‚ 2‚ 1… Ta-da!'",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.9999996186,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-04.m4a",
          "delay": 8400.000381400005
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_clap-03.m4a",
          "delay": 8900.000381400005
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_popper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8000.000381399999
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 95.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_01-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "（手品サークルで、大勢のお客さんに華麗な）\n（マジックを見せるの！　これも凄くかっこいいわ！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（In the magic club‚ I will show off some amazing magic）\n（to many guests! This is also really cool!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.7666678112,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_library-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_library-00-noon",
      "startTime": 110.0000015259
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_01-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "（でも、運動系サークルのマネージャーも）\n（一度やってみたかったのよね～）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（But‚ I also want to try being）\n（a sports club manager~）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 117.7499960584
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_01-hrk013.m4a",
      "text": "「はい、レモンの蜂蜜漬けよ。きっと元気になるわ！\nあ、血が出てる。手当てさせてね。痛いのとんでけー」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "'Here it is‚ honey-marinated lemons. They'll cheer you up!\nAh‚ you're bleeding. Let me support you. Pain‚ go awayー'",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.7999960584,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 133.0333283744
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_01-hrk014.m4a",
      "text": "（それから、頼れる美人マネージャー佐伯遙子の噂は）\n（他校にも広がり有名に！　告白の嵐でモテ期到来ね！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（After that‚ the rumor about the reliable and beautiful manager‚ Haruko Saeki）\n（spreads to other schools and she becomes famous! A storm of confessions brings about a popularity explosion!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.0333283744,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 144.0333283744
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_01-hrk015.m4a",
      "text": "「美人マネージャーなんて、そんなことないわよ～\nみんな褒め過ぎなんだから！　え？　話がある？」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "'A beautiful manager‚ isn't that so~\nEveryone's praising me‚ too much! Huh? Do you have something to say?'",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.0333283744,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 156.4333232881
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_01-hrk016.m4a",
      "text": "「……ありがとうね……私を好きって言ってくれて\nあなたの気持ちは凄く嬉しいわ」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "'…Thank you… for telling me you like me\nI'm very happy about your feelings'",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.4333232881,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_01-hrk017.m4a",
      "text": "「でも……私、心に決めた人がいるの……！」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "'But… I‚ have someone in my heart…!'",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.5333263398,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_library-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_library-00-noon",
      "startTime": 171.6833365124
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_01-hrk018.m4a",
      "text": "やだもー！　そんなに求められても、遙子困っちゃう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Noー! Even if you say you want it that way‚ Haruko is in trouble!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.7333365124,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_library-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_library-00-noon",
      "startTime": 179.6000061035
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_library-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_library-00-noon",
      "startTime": 181.700003179
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_01-hrk019.m4a",
      "text": "あ……すみません……\n声に出ちゃってたわね……うう、恥ずかしい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… I'm sorry…\nMy voice came out… ugh‚ how embarrassing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 181.700003179,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}